naive_mean.method: Simple average of all judge scores (no scaling)

linear_scaling_mean.method: Mean of judges scaled proportionally from [0-4] to [0-10]

best_judge_linear_scaling.method: Best single judge with proportional scaling: Conciseness / Efficiency

ultrafeedback_4judge.method: UltraFeedback 4-judge subset (Truthfulness, Helpfulness, Honesty, Instruction Following)
ultrafeedback_4judge.approach: Proportional scaling of 4 UltraFeedback judges from [0-4] to [0-10]

standardscaler_lr_mean.method: Mean of judges with StandardScaler + LinearRegression

best_judge_standardscaler_lr.method: Best single judge with StandardScaler + LinearRegression: Logical Consistency / Reasoning
